note:
Decrease MaxTP by 25%.
On the 5th stack, reset stack and lose all tp.
<Category: debuff>
<Custom Apply Effect>
var get = a.getStateCounter(3)||0;
get += 1;
a.setStateCounter(3, get);
if(get>=5){  
  var gain = a.tp;
  a.getEntity().addTextIconPopup("-"+gain,4,0);
  a.gainTp(-gain);
  a.setStateCounter(3, 0);
}
</Custom Apply Effect>
<Custom Remove Effect>
a.setStateCounter(3, 0);
</Custom Remove Effect>

Lower MaxHp by 25%.
When hit, lose 5 hp.
Does 10% of MaxHp of Damage on apply.
<Category: debuff>
<Custom React Effect>
if(value>0){
  b.getEntity().addTextIconPopup("-5",0,3);
  b.gainHp(-5);
}
</Custom React Effect>
<Custom Apply Effect>
a.gainHp(-Math.floor(a.mhp*0.1));
</Custom Apply Effect>

Randomly move 1 square at turn end. 
-10% Armor at turn end.
-10% Armor on apply.
<Category: debuff>
<Custom Turn End Effect>
a = this.getEntity();
a.addTextIconPopup("Confuse",0,19);
var x = a._cellX;
var y = a._cellY;
switch(Math.randomInt(4)) {
  case 0:
    x += 1
    break;
  case 1:
    x -= 1;
    break;
  case 2:
    y += 1; 
    break;
  default:
    y -= 1;
};
cell = BattleManagerTBS.getCellAt(x, y);
a.forcePush(a, cell, 1, null, false);

if(this.mp > 0){
  var get = this.mp;
  var degrade = Math.floor(get*0.1);
  a.addTextIconPopup("-"+degrade,0,39);
  this.setMp(get-degrade);
}
</Custom Turn End Effect>
<Custom Apply Effect>
if(this.mp > 0){
  var get = this.mp;
  var degrade = Math.floor(get*0.1);
  a.getEntity().addTextIconPopup("-"+degrade,0,39);
  this.setMp(get-degrade);
}
</Custom Apply Effect>

